---
title: Herby Turkey Sandwiches and Cranberry Sauce with Sweet Potato Wedges and Tangy Mayo Dip
description: Elements of your favourite holiday feast come together between stuffing-inspired garlic toasts with a sweet cranberry sauce and herbed turkey patties. Grainy mustard-mayo adds tang, both in the sandwich and as a dipper for the sweet potato fries.
